synopsis.value:
Non-critpath. Two giant spiders trap the player. The one that shoots the web is female. Her companion is her brother.  The player has a chance to convince the spiders they are friendly, setting the spiders loose on the goblins in the camp above. 

Vocal note: these spiders should sound like aristocratic children. No contractions unless specified in the text.
